    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgyOpySWXWVrzsFC2zFUQqmc",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "我自己用下来也发现了根本问题——Obsidian 不适合流动。手机刷到好内容，根本不可能随手存进去。而且 OpenClaw 虽然能读 Obsidian，但往里面写很危险，双向链接一断就全坏了。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "block_id": "doxlgNRkaYsZEmRPMmGB9tuB6Fc",
      "block_type": 2,
      "block_type_name": "text",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text_run",
          "content": "所以只能单向读，AI 帮不了你管理。内容的整理负担还是全在自己身上。",
          "style": {
            "bold": false,
            "inline_code": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false
          }
        }
      ]
    },
